OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with variable cloud and
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Some prolonged spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine for many into the afternoon.
OL,9,FTemperatures will be near average or
OL,10,Fslightly above. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry with variable
OL,13,Fcloud and clear spells for many. The
OL,14,Fodd mist or fog patch is possible in
OL,15,Fsome rural spots. Generally a mild
OL,16,Fnight, with light winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FStaying fine and dry, with
OL,19,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells
OL,20,Fthroughout the day. Feeling warm in
OL,21,Fthe sunshine, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
